      Some prescription assistance programs are available to help cover drugs
      needed to treat specific conditions or diseases. Select from the list
      below any conditions or diseases for which you currently or will soon
      be taking medications. You can select one or more conditions.

        Please select up to five conditions or diseases from the list below:
        (Please read the Important Note above for multiple searches)
        [ ] Amyotrophic Lateral Sclerosis
        [ ] Blepharospasm, Hemi-facial spasm and Strabismus
        [ ] Blood Cancer
        [ ] Carnitine Deficiency
        [ ] Kidney Disease
        [ ] Multiple Sclerosis
        [ ] Myasthenia Gravis
        [ ] Nephropathic Cystinosis


